{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_10_01",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 1話 風邪引きますよー",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（トリエルが、人気アニメを原作とする舞台の）\n（主演に決まった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（TRINITYAiLE has been chosen for the lead role in a stage play）\n（based on a popular anime.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（舞台はいつものステージと勝手が違うし、大変だろう）\n（俺も頑張ってサポートしていかないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（A stage play is different from their usual performances‚ so it'll be tough.）\n（I should do my best to support them too.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.1761223634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、ふふーん……\nあ！　{user}さん、お疲れ様です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm~‚ hmm hmm~…\nAh! {user}-san‚ good work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 157.21096990000126,
          "startTime": 12.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.5378453732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……って、あれ、どうしたんですか？\nなんだか、ちょっと疲れた顔してるみたいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ hello? What's wrong?\nSomehow‚ you look a bit tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか？　最近、仕事が立て込んでるせいで\nそう見えるのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I? Maybe it's because work has been piling up lately‚\nso I might look that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 31.8422226746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それよりすみれこそ、舞台の準備と並行して各局の番組\nにもひっぱりだこで疲れが溜まってるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More than that‚ Sumire‚ you're preparing for the stage while also\nbeing in demand for TV shows. Aren't you getting tired?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.9322227001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……スケジュールが詰まってますし\n移動中も台本読み込んでて、大変は大変ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… my schedule is packed‚\nand I even read scripts while traveling‚ so it is tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも子役でドラマに出てた頃も、クランクインした後は\n稽古と撮影を繰り返すのが普通でしたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I was a child actor in dramas‚ once filming began‚\nit was normal to just keep repeating rehearsals and shooting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 56.5070527871
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、すみれは演技の仕事も沢山経験してるもんな\nこういう状況は慣れっこか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ Sumire has lots of experience with acting work.\nSo you're used to situations like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい。お芝居の仕事も好きですし\nそれに今回は、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんも一緒ですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I love acting work too‚\nand this time‚ Rui-chan and Yu-chan are with me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 71.0572800795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "三人で一緒にお芝居の舞台に立てるのが嬉しくて\nそのためなら、疲れたなんて言ってられません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm happy that the three of us can perform on stage together.\nFor that‚ I can't complain about being tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 78.2810273647
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうそう。役作りのヒントになるかと思って\nお医者さんや看護師さんのエッセイも読んでるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right. I thought it might help with my role preparation‚\nso I’ve also been reading essays by doctors and nurses.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "原作のアニメは、『癒やし』と『優しさ』がテーマだと\n優ちゃんが力説してましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan passionately explained that the original anime's\nthemes are \"healing\" and \"kindness.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9125738879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 92.3972401141
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "特に私がやるキャラは、両親がお医者さんで\n本人も将来は看護師になりたいって女の子ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially the character I'm playing has doctor parents‚\nand she's a girl who wants to become a nurse in the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "その子が目指しているものを\n私もちゃんと、分かっていないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to properly understand\nwhat she's aiming for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 105.0954488913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "すみれはこの間の映画でもいい演技だったもんな\n役作りにはそういう地道な準備が大事なんだなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire's acting in the recent movie was good too.\nI guess that kind of steady preparation is really important for role preparation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 113.5124782085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "そんな、たいしたことじゃないですよ\nそれにエッセイは、仕事抜きでもいい本でしたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not such a big deal.\nBesides‚ the essays were good books even aside from work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "患者さんの心に寄り添って、病気が治るまで支える……\n看護師さんって、人を助ける仕事って凄いですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Supporting patients emotionally until their illness heals…\nBeing a nurse is… helping people is such an amazing job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 130.1122432232
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "役だけじゃなくて、私自身も\nいつかはそういう、人を助けられる人になりたいなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And it’s not only for the role‚ I also\nwant to become someone who can help others someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1333482106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 137.8307012398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今だって、すみれ達の歌はみんなを元気に出来てるよ\nでも、いくら楽しくても、あまり無理はしないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even now‚ your songs can cheer everyone up.\nBut no matter how fun it is‚ don't overdo it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6000148773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "はい、お気遣いありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ thank you for your concern!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.9053266048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 151.1000000953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（しかし、すみれが張り切っていた舞台の仕事には）\n（次第に、暗雲が垂れ込め始めた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（However‚ dark clouds began to gather over the stage work）\n（that Sumire was so enthusiastic about.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6333624522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……私、どうしたらいいんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… what should I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9416960556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、優がそこまで演技が苦手だったなんてな\n有名俳優の娘だからか、本人も自信満々だったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought Yu would be that bad at acting.\nMaybe because she's a famous actress's daughter‚ she was very confident though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.3990201155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "はい。今日も演出家さんからダメ出しの嵐でした\n本番までこのままなら、舞台は中止とまで言われて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Today as well‚ the director gave her a barrage of harsh criticism.\nHe even said the play would be canceled if things continue like this until opening night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.7667008717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃん自身が、一番落ち込んじゃって\n「原作にもトリエルにも泥を塗ってしまう」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan herself is the most discouraged‚\nsaying \"I'll tarnish both the original work and TRINITYAiLE\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.6333614349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "今まで、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんに助けてもらったから\n今度はお芝居の先輩として、私が助ける番なのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until now‚ Rui-chan and Yu-chan have helped me‚\nso this time‚ as a senior in acting‚ it's my turn to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.2666947682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "子役の頃に教わった演技のコツとか\n演技のメソッドの実践とか、いろいろ教えたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I taught her acting tips I learned as a child actor‚\nand had her try out different acting methods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.4333526611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "いざ優ちゃんにやってもらうと、うまくいかなくて……\n他に私が出来ることって、何があるかなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but‚ when Yu-chan actually tried them‚ it just didn’t work out…\nI wonder what else I can do for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.1333614349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なぁ、すみれ。すみれが力になりたいのも分かるが\nこれは優の仕事で、優が向き合わないといけない問題だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Sumire. I understand you want to help‚ but\nthis is Yu's job‚ and a problem Yu has to face.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.0000281016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すみれが全部抱え込む必要はないし\n優にはお母さんもついてる。俺達は信じて待とう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't need to take everything on yourself‚\nand Yu has her mother with her. Let's believe and wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.2259664024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね\nこの舞台を一番楽しみにしてたのは優ちゃんですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right.\nYu-chan was looking forward to this stage the most‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.3666947682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr022.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんがこのまま\nへこたれて、終わる訳ないですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and there's no way\nYu-chan will just give up and quit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.2000281016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。すみれが今やるべきことは\n万全の体制で舞台に立てるように、備えておくことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. What you should do now is\nprepare yourself to stand on stage in the best possible condition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.0666947682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "特に最近、風邪も流行ってるみたいだし\n不安になり過ぎて、体調まで崩すのが一番良くない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially since colds seem to be going around lately‚\ngetting too anxious and ruining your health would be the worst.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.7000281016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（とはいえ、すみれは真面目だからなぁ）\n（思い詰めないように、俺も注意して見ていないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That said‚ Sumire is so earnest…）\n（I need to watch carefully so she doesn't brood too much.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.3000281016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
